## Description {#details}

Represents a YAML map created from either a block map for a flow map.

This parses the YAML stream as increment() is called.

Example: Name: &#95;main Scope: Global

Definition at line 419 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/support/yamlparser-h">YAMLParser.h</a>.
